c: 24
v: 54
t: "Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Nimwumvire Allah munumvire Intumwa, ariko nimuhakana (mumenye ko) iyo ntumwa izabazwa ibyo yashinzwe, namwe mukabazwa ibyo mwashinzwe.” Nyamara nimuramuka muyumviye muzaba muyobotse. Nta kindi Intumwa ishinzwe kitari ugusohoza ubutumwa mu buryo bugaragara gusa"